[[es:articulate]] [[fa:articulate]] [[fr:articulate]] [[io:articulate]] [[pl:articulate]] [[ru:articulate]] [[vi:articulate]] [[tr:articulate]] [[zh:articulate]]
===Innapropriate use=== In 2007, it was popular opinion that a caucasian person calling an african-american person "articulate" was offensive and racist. A famous incident occurred when U.S. Senator Joseph Biden called U.S. Senator Barack Obama "who is articulate and bright and clean and a nice-looking guy." African-Ammerican civil rights activits condemned Senator Biden and demanded an apology.

